{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Purchase more heart-lung machines to fight Covid-19 coronavirus",
        "additional_details": "We want the Government to: \r\n1) Publish how many ventilators, heart-lung machines & ECMO beds they will purchase!\r\n2) Publish when they will purchase them.\r\n3) Publish the date those machines will enter service.\r\n4) Actually follow through and buy the machines.\r\nBasically: we want them to accept the BMA's position that we don't have enough and put the required funding behind an order for those machines to rectify the short-fall as soon as possible.\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jdDl2g7F4tU",
        "background": "Ministers need to drastically ramp up the purchase of ventilators and Heart-Lung machines and ECMO beds. The machines are an essential part of treating those with severe cases of COVID-19, when a sticky mucus fills patients' lungs preventing them from breathing.",
